      "value": "Field semantics — content format"
    },
    {
      "fieldId": "1a000002-0000-4000-a000-000000000002",
      "value": "**38.** `Field.contentFormat`, when present, is only meaningful when `valueType` is `\"string\"` or `\"text\"`. Implementations must ignore `contentFormat` on fields with any other `valueType`."
    }
